ZH: 我委托了朋友照看我的宠物。
EN: I entrusted my friend with taking care of my pet.

ZH: 他委托我给他寄信。
EN: He entrusted me with sending the letter for him.

ZH: 这个公司委托我来处理合同。
EN: This company entrusted me with handling the contract.

ZH: 我将这个任务委托给了一个专业的团队。
EN: I entrusted this task to a professional team.

ZH: 她委托妹妹代表她参加会议。
EN: She entrusted her sister to attend the meeting on her behalf.

ZH: 我们可以委托你为我们寻找合适的房子吗？
EN: Can we entrust you to find a suitable house for us?

ZH: 他委托我代表他在会上发言。
EN: He entrusted me to speak on his behalf at the meeting.

ZH: 雇主委托我为公司招聘新员工。
EN: The employer entrusts me with recruiting new employees for the company.

ZH: 我们委托专业律师处理这个案件。
EN: We entrust professional lawyers to handle this case.

ZH: 我们将这个项目的管理委托给了外部顾问。
EN: We entrusted the management of this project to external consultants.

ZH: 委托书上有你的签名吗？
EN: Is your signature on the letter of entrustment?

ZH: 请你委托他给我们带来些水果。
EN: Please ask him to bring us some fruits on your behalf.

ZH: 她委托他帮忙安排旅行的细节。
EN: She entrusted him to help arrange the details of the trip.

ZH: 你可以委托我购买机票。
EN: You can entrust me with purchasing the plane tickets.

ZH: 我感到荣幸被委托为这个重要项目的负责人。
EN: I feel honored to be entrusted as the head of this important project.

ZH: 他们将委托给你一项重要的任务。
EN: They will entrust you with an important task.

ZH: 请将这个包裹委托快递送出去。
EN: Please entrust the package to the courier for delivery.

ZH: 我们委托你负责制定新的营销策略。
EN: We entrust you with the responsibility of developing new marketing strategies.

ZH: 他委托我给他找一个靠谱的租房代理。
EN: He entrusted me with finding a reliable rental agent for him.

ZH: 我们需要委托一家专业机构来进行市场调查。
EN: We need to entrust a professional agency to conduct market research.
